{
  "stem": "11205.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not-- not very much because we lived in a-- in a place where mostly it wasn't met too many Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, Jewish people, they had their quotas, that used to call [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there, only Jews lived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But where I lived, it was mostly Polish people, so I-- we mix-- we mixed well.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Only once, I coming home from school, and a little boy poured a bucket of water over me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was the only incident.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Otherwise, I couldn't--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I feel-- How I felt?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I felt really Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was autumn.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I came home soaking wet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- what-- what could they say, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we knew because they-- it-- it use-- it came a lot of German people, which they brought to the border, you know, ex-Polish citizen.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They broke through the border and let them in, so it was already quite a few in Chelm.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they'd been telling-- but still, they-- they didn't believe is something wrong, and they, you know, they came only dressed whatever they had on, and the Jewish communities start to make collections for them.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's what all-- all we knew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Otherwise, it-- nobody believed because even my father-- Chelm was under-- in the First World War was under Austria, and in this building where we lived was a lot of Austrians people living.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father was-- was [INAUDIBLE] at home, I remember he had the big picture with all those people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They used to be together, and he-- he was prizing them, and I remember he used to say, it's impossible.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They are good people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's impossible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He-- they didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's what kept him, because he could-- the family could all got-- got over the border.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Russia.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
